================================================================================
Attribution policy for ported code
================================================================================

Every source file in /src/ whose content is wholly or partially derived from
an upstream project must begin with a header comment identifying:

  1. The upstream project name.
  2. The upstream file path.
  3. The upstream commit SHA at the time of porting.
  4. The upstream license.
  5. A short note about what was changed (paraphrased/rewritten/unchanged).

Example:
  /*
   *  Ported from: CoplayDev/unity-mcp
   *  Path:        MCPForUnity/Editor/Tools/Animation/AnimatorRead.cs
   *  Commit:      <sha>
   *  License:     MIT (see /third_party/coplay-LICENSE.md)
   *  Changes:     Extracted structured-state projection; dropped screenshot hook.
   */
